'''美國兒科學會'''（{{lang-en|American Academy of Pediatrics，簡稱AAP}}）是美國的[[兒科|兒科]]研究學會，總部位於[[伊利諾伊州|伊利諾伊州]]{{le|埃爾克格羅夫村|Elk Grove Village}}，並在[[華盛頓特區|華盛頓特區]]設有辦公室<ref name=AAP_contact_us>{{cite web| url=http://www2.aap.org/visit/contact.htm| title=Contacting the American Academy of Pediatrics| publisher=American Academy of Pediatrics| date=2004-05-25| accessdate=2013-03-30| archive-date=2013-03-31| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130331055841/http://www2.aap.org/visit/contact.htm| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 沿革 ==
該學會由35名兒科醫生於1930年成立，以確立兒童衞生保健標準為宗旨<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www2.aap.org/pediatrichistorycenter/PHCHistory.htm| title=Pediatric History Center| publisher=American Academy of Pediatrics| accessdate=2013-03-30| archive-date=2013-02-21| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130221140136/http://www2.aap.org/pediatrichistorycenter/PHCHistory.htm| dead-url=yes}}</ref>，目前擁有約6萬4000名會員<ref name="Membership">{{cite web| url=http://www.aap.org/en-us/about-the-aap/aap-facts/Pages/AAP-Facts.aspx#Membership| title=AAP Facts: Membership| publisher=American Academy of Pediatrics| accessdate=2016-05-10| archive-date=2019-05-28| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190528135227/http://www.aap.org/en-us/about-the-aap/aap-facts/Pages/AAP-Facts.aspx#Membership| dead-url=no}}</ref>，以及約390名員工。美國兒科學會還擁有世界上最大的兒科出版體系，出版物包括電子產品、專業文獻、醫學教材、實踐管理出版物、患者育材料和育兒書籍等<ref>{{cite web| title=AAP Facts: Publications| url=http://www.aap.org/en-us/about-the-aap/aap-facts/Pages/AAP-Facts.aspx#Publications| publisher=American Academy of Pediatrics| accessdate=2013-03-30| archive-date=2019-05-28| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190528135227/http://www.aap.org/en-us/about-the-aap/aap-facts/Pages/AAP-Facts.aspx#Publications| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

值得注意的是，有六萬餘名會員的美國兒科學會出於學術專業而支持同性伴侶收養，擁有五百名會員的基督教信仰倡議團體「[[美國兒科醫學院|美國兒科醫學院]]」（American College of Pediatricians，簡稱ACPeds）<ref name=catexch>{{cite web | url = http://catholicexchange.com/2003/07/30/90378/ | title = Pro-Life Pediatric Group Stands Contrary to the American Academy of Pediatrics | publisher = Catholic Exchange | date = July 30, 2003 | access-date = 2016-11-29 | archive-date = 2011-07-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110723141108/http://catholicexchange.com/2003/07/30/90378/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>則因為基督教信仰因素反對同性伴侶收養。兩者名稱極易混淆，實乃不同團體。

